            "title": "綠城中國首季合同銷售按年降逾29%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">綠城中國(03900)公布，今年首季取得合同銷售約256億元(人民幣．下同)，較去年同期的363億元減少29.48%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：綠城中國官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/08/20230825_FI_source-web_綠城中國-杭州紫棠園實景圖.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：綠城中國官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/08/20230825_FI_source-web_綠城中國-杭州紫棠園實景圖.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：綠城中國官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">上述銷售涉及樓面約82萬平方米，歸屬於綠城集團的權益銷售金額約177億元，較去年同期的238億元也減少25.63%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">單計3月份，綠城集團自投項目取得銷售2840套，總樓面約42萬平方米，銷售額約151億元，較去年同期的218億元減少30.73%，均價每平方米約3.6萬元。截至3月底，尚有累計已簽認購協議未轉銷售合同的金額約31億元，歸屬綠城集團的權益金額約22億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">再加上綠城集團代建項目在首季錄得累計銷售約130億元，綠城集團期內總合同銷售約386億元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15855081-%e7%b6%a0%e5%9f%8e%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b%e9%a6%96%e5%ad%a3%e5%90%88%e5%90%8c%e9%8a%b7%e5%94%ae%e6%8c%89%e5%b9%b4%e9%99%8d%e9%80%be29",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20230825_FI_source-web_03900_GREENTOWN_FB.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-10 08:56:25",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "鈞達股份首季扭虧為盈 賺1416.36萬元人幣",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">鈞達股份(02865)公布按中國會計準則的今年首季業績，已扭虧為盈，錄得歸屬上市公司股東淨利潤1416.36萬元(人民幣．下同)。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"鈞達新能源官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/JTPV-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"鈞達新能源官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/JTPV-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">鈞達新能源官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">去年同期該公司尚有淨虧損1.06億元。不過，若按照扣除非經常性損益後歸屬上市公司股東損益，該公司今年首季仍錄淨虧損4350.32萬元，虧損按年收窄79.97%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">該公司指出，首季業績改善，主要因為電池片銷售單價提升。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15855064-%e9%88%9e%e9%81%94%e8%82%a1%e4%bb%bd%e9%a6%96%e5%ad%a3%e6%89%ad%e8%99%a7%e7%82%ba%e7%9b%88-%e8%b3%ba1416-36%e8%90%ac%e5%85%83%e4%ba%ba%e5%b9%a3",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/12/02865.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-10 08:42:16",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "中國金茂首季簽約銷售按年增逾22%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">中國金茂(00817)公布，在今年首季錄得累計簽約銷售合共224.28億元(人民幣．下同)，較去年同期的183.02億元增加22.54%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：中國金茂官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/10/20240105_PO__source-web_.jpeg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中國金茂官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/10/20240105_PO__source-web_.jpeg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：中國金茂官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">上述銷售涉及樓面96.3萬平方米，包括長沙梅溪湖國際新城等多個項目。單計3月份，簽約銷售也達94.98億元，較去年同期的71.91億元增加32.08%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">截至3月底，該公司尚錄得已認購但未簽約物業銷售6.84億元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15855038-%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b%e9%87%91%e8%8c%82%e9%a6%96%e5%ad%a3%e7%b0%bd%e7%b4%84%e9%8a%b7%e5%94%ae%e6%8c%89%e5%b9%b4%e5%a2%9e%e9%80%be22",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/00817.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-10 08:36:28",
